dct_title_s: Grundriss von Jerusalem, nach dem Josephus und den Rabbinen
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, places of historical interest; plan of Jerusalem.
"A.W.H. Th. IX." -- top right corner ; "A" -- bottom right corner.
Includes index: [Sites and structures of interest].
